title: Episode 36 w/ Mystikal
itunes:title: Episode 36 w/ Mystikal
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up with Mystikal. The New Orleans legend talks about working with No Limit Records, Cash Money and his early influences. On this episode the guys get Busta Rhymes on the phone to lock in his future episode. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
